## Architecture

```
Bridge (backend) → useBridge()/useSSE() → Stores (Pinia) → localStorage → Components (Vue 3)
```

## Key Patterns

- Reactive state: Vue ref()/computed() in all stores
- Watch-based persistence: backlog/chat → localStorage
- Project scoping: all stores reload on projectStore.selectedId change
- SSE streaming: cancelable, typed StreamEvent (text|tool_use|permission_request)
- Admin guards: router.beforeEach checks auth.role
- All pages lazy-loaded via dynamic imports

